sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server

    Server->>Server: Generate X25519 key pair
    Server->>Server: Generate ML-KEM key pair
    Server-->>Client: Send X25519 public key
    Server-->>Client: Send ML-KEM public key
    Server-->>Client: Send hybrid certificate
    Client->>Client: Validate hybrid certificate
    Client->>Client: Generate X25519 ephemeral key pair
    Client->>Client: Compute X25519 shared secret
    Client->>Client: ML-KEM encapsulation
    Client->>Client: Derive hybrid secret with HKDF
    Client-->>Server: Send X25519 client public key
    Client-->>Server: Send ML-KEM ciphertext
    Server->>Server: Compute X25519 shared secret
    Server->>Server: ML-KEM decapsulation
    Server->>Server: Derive hybrid secret with HKDF
    Client-->>Server: Secure communication using hybrid secret
